CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FA landmark trial aiming to shape the
OL,7,Ffuture of prostate cancer screening in
OL,8,Fthe UK has begun testing a group of
OL,9,Fmen considered to be at the highest
OL,10,Frisk of developing the disease.
OL,12,FThe Transform trial, funded by
OL,13,FProstate Cancer UK and the National
OL,14,FInstitute for Health and Care Research
OL,15,F(NIHR), will try out a combination of
OL,16,Ftests - such as genetic spit tests,
OL,17,Fblood tests, or 10-minute MRI scans `
OL,18,Fto see which is most effective at
OL,19,Fdetecting the disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FIt will focus on men at the highest
OL,7,Frisk, such as Black men, and could
OL,8,Fproduce game-changing results in as
OL,9,Flittle as two years.
OL,11,FBlack men face double the risk of
OL,12,Fdeveloping and dying from prostate
OL,13,Fcancer, the chief executive officer of
OL,14,Fthe NIHR said, describing the start of
OL,15,Fthe trial as a "huge moment".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,F"The team is working closely with
OL,7,FBlack community leaders and
OL,8,Forganisations as part of our
OL,9,Fcommitment to ensure meaningful
OL,10,Fparticipation in research among
OL,11,Feveryone in our society," Professor
OL,12,FLucy Chappell said.
OL,14,FAt first, the trial will test new
OL,15,Ftechniques against current NHS
OL,16,Fmethods, before then taking the best
OL,17,Fmethods forward to testing in a group
OL,18,Fof up to 300,000 men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"If taking part helps move us closer
OL,12,Fto having a proper screening programme
OL,13,Fin the future, so men are just invited
OL,14,Fby their GP like they are for other
OL,15,Fcancers, that would make such a
OL,16,Fdifference," said Jaroslaw Galik, 55,
OL,17,Fwho was one of the first men tested at
OL,18,Fthe InHealth community diagnostic
OL,19,Fcentre in Ealing, west London, on
OL,20,FTuesday.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,F"To think that just by taking a couple
OL,7,Fof tests I could be helping to finally
OL,8,Fget to screening and save thousands of
OL,9,Flives is incredible."
OL,11,FProstate cancer is curable if found
OL,12,Fearly, but without a screening
OL,13,Fprogramme, early diagnosis relies on
OL,14,Fmen understanding the risk and
OL,15,Fspeaking to their GP - which most only
OL,16,Fdo once they have symptoms.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
