FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FEarly diagnosis rates vary widely
OL,7,Facross the UK, with men in more
OL,8,Fdeprived areas 29% more likely to be
OL,9,Fdiagnosed late compared to more
OL,10,Faffluent areas, according to the NIHR.
OL,12,FNearly a third of men diagnosed in
OL,13,FScotland have incurable stage 4
OL,14,Fcancer, compared to 21% in England.
OL,16,FThe UK national screening committee
OL,17,F(UKNSC), which advises ministers and
OL,18,Fthe NHS on all aspects of screening,
OL,19,Fhas agreed to review any new evidence
OL,20,Ffrom the Transform trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
