FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FThe UKNSC published final guidance
OL,7,Fthis week on detecting prostate cancer
OL,8,Fand advised that a prostate specific
OL,9,Fantigen (PSA) test - a type of blood
OL,10,Ftest - should not be used in
OL,11,Fpopulation-wide screening as it is "
OL,12,Flikely to cause more harm than good".
OL,14,FThe reliability of such tests have
OL,15,Fbeen questioned by some experts, as
OL,16,Fmen with a high PSA level may not have
OL,17,Fcancer and some men with cancer have a
OL,18,Fnormal PSA result.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,FThe committee instead recommended only
OL,7,Fscreening men with BRCA1 and BRCA2
OL,8,Fgenetic mutations ` which put them at
OL,9,Fa far higher risk of prostate cancer `
OL,10,Fevery two years, between the ages of
OL,11,F45 and 61.
OL,13,F"Men across the country are crying out
OL,14,Ffor a screening programme and we're
OL,15,Fcommitted to building a future where
OL,16,Fevery man gets that chance," said
OL,17,FLaura Kerby, chief executive of
OL,18,FProstate Cancer UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,F"That is why we have driven the
OL,7,Fdevelopment of Transform and funded
OL,8,Fthe #42 million programme, alongside
OL,9,Fthe NIHR.
OL,11,F"We know that a safe and effective
OL,12,Fmass screening programme could save
OL,13,Fthousands of men's lives and it starts
OL,14,Fwith these men walking through the
OL,15,Fdoor today and trialling these tests."
OL,17,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting called
OL,18,Fthe trial the "most ambitious prostate
OL,19,Fcancer research programme in a
OL,20,Fgeneration",
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774386358
OL,3,CFirst men tested in landmark UK
OL,4,Cprostate cancer screening trial
OL,6,F"The evidence it generates will be
OL,7,Fcrucial in shaping how we screen for
OL,8,Fthis disease for decades to come,"
OL,9,FStreeting said.
OL,11,FScotland has also launched a prostate
OL,12,Fcancer initiative on Tuesday, offering
OL,13,Ffree PSA tests to men aged from 40 to
OL,14,F80, and taking further blood samples
OL,15,Ffor research.
OL,17,FStarting in Glasgow, the Scottish
OL,18,FProstate Cancer Initiative will host
OL,19,Fpop-up events throughout the Scotland,
OL,20,Fwith men advised to register online.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
